DataElement.preferredDefinition: The spatial outline of an object as described by the configuration of straight or curved lines.:Having, relating to, or consisting of more than one individual, element, part, or other component; manifold. (dictionary.com):A mark that is long relative to its width; a length (straight or curved) without breadth or thickness; the trace of a moving point._A mark that is long relative to its width; a length (straight or curved) without breadth or thickness; the trace of a moving point.:The appearance of objects (or light sources) described in terms of a person's perception of their hue and lightness (or brightness) and saturation._Character string datatype stands for text data.
